    <note>Yang(2) Anzhi [22638] The SongYuan xuean identifies him as a son of Yang(2) Shi [2022], but Yang Shi, WJ, 30.3b has him as the second son of an unnamed Yang(2) member of a distinguished lineage (youzu) of Jiangxi. His younger brother, and #6 son of this unnamed Yang(2), became a buddhist monk called Zhengzhen. The funerary inscription is for his mother, surnamed Zhang(1), who was from a Nankang jun, Jianchang county lineage. CBD, 4, 3161.</note>
